sequenceDiagram
  participant App as 应用
  participant GW as AI Gateway
  participant S as 推理服务
  participant E as 推理引擎
  participant G as GPU
  App->>GW: Chat 请求(messages, stream=true)
  GW->>S: 鉴权、限流、路由后转发
  S->>E: tokenizer + 入队
  E->>G: prefill 输入上下文
  G-->>E: KV Cache 初始化完成
  loop 每个输出 token
    E->>G: decode step
    G-->>E: next token
    E-->>S: token
    S-->>App: streaming chunk
  end
  S->>GW: token 计量与 trace
